        div(class="flex flex-col gap-2 justify-center items-center  mt-6")    
            h1(class="text-3xl text-white uppercase font-bold bg-black bg-opacity-80 px-3 py-2 rounded-md") @vigilio/express
            p(class="text-white")
                | <b>@vigilio/express </b> is a fullstack framework to create web apps
            span(class="text-2xl uppercase font-bold text-yellow-400") OUT NOW THE BETA!!!      
        div( class="bg-black my-6 p-4 bg-opacity-40 w-[300px] mx-auto rounded-md" )
